Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is excited to present to the market for sale Unit 4/185 Beverley Street, Morningside. Morningside is situated approx. 6 radial kilometres south east of the Brisbane CBD and enjoys close proximity to the Port precinct and Gateway Arterial which offers easy access to north and south coast arterials. Morningside offers close proximity to transport services and shopping facilities whilst being centrally located within the prime Gateway Industrial Precinct.

4/185 Beverley Street, Morningside is a modern, tilt panel industrial unit boasting huge main road exposure to Lytton Road. Currently set up as a wholesale coffee operation with a fully approved café & commercial kitchen; this is an opportunity not to be missed! Some of the features of this investment include:

•	Total floor area of 226sqm - office/warehouse/retail/café & kitchen
•	Opportunity to purchase as an investment with a lease in place or purchase building and business together
•	Unit offers huge exposure to main Lytton Road generating significant business opportunity
•	Fully set up as a wholesale coffee operation with a fully approved café & commercial kitchen

4/185 Beverley Street, Morningside is being offered for sale via Expressions of Interest closing 9th September 2020 at 4pm.

For further information surrounding this unique investment opportunity, please contact Exclusive Agent, Ben Lyons of CBRE today!

- 80sqm - 175sqm tenancy
- Choice of two floors or whole 7 months half rent (conditions apply)
- Ready to occupy
- Net effective rate now $300 per sqm (GST excl)
- Owner will fit meeting room
- Owner will fit phone points, data and power
- Good parking

For more information or to arrange an inspection, please contact CB Richard Ellis agents:
Sam Higgins - 0439 034 045
Nick Witheriff - 0405 618 477

Common.Highlight.Common.Text: Modern corporate office over two levels

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
The property is located within one of the most tightly held precincts of Morningside, only minutes away from Oxford Street precinct, entrance to the Gateway Motorway and approx. 7 radial kilometres south-east of the Brisbane CBD. This location is ideal for any business based on the Southern and Eastern fringes of the city who are looking to acquire functional office and storage facilities without the city fringe price tag.

This outstanding corporate office offers the following key
features:

+ 190sqm of Modern corporate office accommodation split over two levels
+ Both levels are fully self-contained and provides any buyer the ability to leave as split tenancies or convert back to a whole
+ Top floor currently leased on a 3 year deal providing a rental return of $26,500 p.a.
+ Ability to occupy or invest 
+ Tightly held complex 
+ 6 Exclusive car parks 

For further information or to arrange your inspection, please
contact Exclusive Agents Jonathan Blake or Ben Lyons
from CBRE.

Common.LongDescription.Common.Text:
CBRE is pleased to present to the market, on behalf of Receivers appointed, for sale via Public Auction onsite, Unit 1/65 Riverside Place, Morningside. 

This offering provides an opportunity to secure a highly desirable office/warehouse strata unit located in the Morningside precinct, a highly sought after location for a range of owner occupiers, investors and tenants. 

Some of the features of this property include:
+ 203sqm* strata titled office/warehouse unit incorporating ground level reception/office and upper level office area
+ Located just off Lytton Road, in close proximity to the Gateway Motorway
+ Container height roller door access

*approximately

For more information or to arrange an inspection please contact the Exclusive Agents.

This neat & tidy industrial unit is one of six units in the complex which is located just off main Lytton Road within a tightly held precinct of Morningside. The unit is highly functional and provides a small mezzanine office and a clearspan warehouse with good internal height. 

The property features the following: 

+	37sqm* mezzanine office
+	186sqm* clear span, high bay warehouse
+	Approved food grade facility
+	Access via container height roller door
+	4 Exclusive car parks

This quality industrial unit can be bought vacant possession or with a lease in place. For further information or to arrange your inspection, please contact Exclusive Agent Ben Lyons of CBRE.

180sqm office/warehouse

* Contains approximately 455sqm of well appointed office with a further 135sqm (approx) of clearspan warehouse.
* Secured hardstand areas
* Competitive rentals!!
* Will suit any small business operators.


For more information please contact Nick Witheriff on 0405 618 477.
